title: Speaker NA enquires after health of Mushtaq Ghani
content:
ISLAMABAD, Jun 14 (APP):Speaker National Assembly Asad Qaiser Sunday called up Speaker Pakhtunkhwa Assembly Mushtaq Ghani and enquired after their health.
The Speaker wished him speedy recovery from the coronavirus disease.
Ghani thanked Asad Qaiser for expressing best wishes for him.
